rows.label: qst701202_msg0001
rows.name:
My master, Thales, went to
Torigo Village on business
and hasn't returned.

rows.label: qst701202_msg0002
rows.name:
I don't think anything has happened,
but if you could check on him...

rows.label: qst701202_msg0003
rows.name:
My master's home is said to be
at the back of Torigo Village.

rows.label: qst701202_msg0004
rows.name:
If you find him, could you
tell him that his apprentice,
Sharla, was worried?

rows.label: qst701202_msg0104
rows.name:
Nox Promontory...? That
might be the place my master
said was his favorite...

rows.label: qst701202_msg0105
rows.name:
I believe he said it was near the
port of Gula, towards the tail.

rows.label: qst701202_msg0106
rows.name: Um... is my master perhaps there?

rows.label: qst701202_msg0201
rows.name:
...Reinforced glass? If
my master were here, he
could prepare it, but...
